{"tid":895959,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★銅鑼灣淪陷！【逼爆SOGO】感謝祭千人堵塞路面等開門","createTime":"2018-11-09T15:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T16:11:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a558302727fea7f7c6fd22f840702547af983ffb","tid":895959,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2072333/org/756d3d4572b2e7e478dd1b2b193f6201.jpg/I1mAKzh8UZNr4VYVsVWUtNH8AKQyxohBytmjBeDZowU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2072333%2Forg%2F756d3d4572b2e7e478dd1b2b193f6201.jpg%2FI1mAKzh8UZNr4VYVsVWUtNH8AKQyxohBytmjBeDZowU&h=6ccd5eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2072326/org/2b2aaa6d4f42dafc350cb26327a1b09d.jpg/6G-cYXdyPnSKGFhun6JfkDyAZQich7JUJPBN5w7wTec\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2072326%2Forg%2F2b2aaa6d4f42dafc350cb26327a1b09d.jpg%2F6G-cYXdyPnSKGFhun6JfkDyAZQich7JUJPBN5w7wTec&h=8a3491e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2072332/org/faf2766225896d41f1340870a47bf363.jpg/wUsDcp0FNLyHJx7fP351XCNneuHj7VtsyjGL7eAxi-0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2072332%2Forg%2Ffaf2766225896d41f1340870a47bf363.jpg%2FwUsDcp0FNLyHJx7fP351XCNneuHj7VtsyjGL7eAxi-0&h=2618d3a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣軒尼詩道SOGO店外有近千人聚集，眾人整裝待發，帶備大型購物袋、行李箱，待SOGO十點開門入場血拼！今日是SOGO感謝周年慶首日舉行，各大品牌推出大量限定優惠，吸引大批市民及內地客前往搶購。由於現場人數太多，警方安排警員到場維持秩序。<br />\n<br />\n記者現場所見，到場購物者以內地客為主，在清晨五時起開門在SOGO門外排隊，當中不乏代購客。早上十時，SOGO開門營業，眾人即湧進商場衝至心儀品牌的櫃台購物，不消一小時，滿載而歸的客人走出行人路盤點戰利品。至早上十時許，受內地客熱愛品牌紛紛「截龍」，如SKII、Est&eacute;e Lauder、SHISEIDO等等。有警察到場維持秩序，並用廣東話呼籲有意購物的市民可以待兩小時後再到場排隊，惟部份內地客疑語言問題聽不懂呼籲，繼續在場排隊。<br />\n<br />\nSOGO門外的街道逼爆排隊客人，店內更是另一個戰場。店內人數眾多，擠得水泄不通、寸步難行，有顧客購買心儀商品後無法離開店舖，唯有雙手抬高戰勝利品緩媛地走出困境。商戶亦忙過不停，不斷拆貨、補貨上架、接待客人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/256967/%E9%80%BC%E7%88%86sogo-%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E7%A5%AD%E5%8D%83%E4%BA%BA%E5%A0%B5%E5%A1%9E%E8%B7%AF%E9%9D%A2%E7%AD%89%E9%96%8B%E9%96%80-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%BB%A3%E8%B3%BC%E5%AE%A2%E9%A0%90%E6%95%B8%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E6%8E%83%E8%B2%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F256967%2F%25E9%2580%25BC%25E7%2588%2586sogo-%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%25AC%259D%25E7%25A5%25AD%25E5%258D%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A0%25B5%25E5%25A1%259E%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%25AD%2589%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%2596%2580-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E9%25A0%2590%25E6%2595%25B8%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%258E%2583%25E8%25B2%25A8&d=1qTZy9M3gJMnvKVqcUQz3jACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=a655423d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/256967/%E9%80%BC%E7%88%86sogo-%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E7%A5%AD%E5%8D%83%E4%BA%BA%E5%A0%B5%E5%A1%9E%E8%B7%AF%E9%9D%A2%E7%AD%89%E9%96%8B%E9%96%80-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%BB%A3%E8%B3%BC%E5%AE%A2%E9%A0%90%E6%95%B8%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E6%8E%83%E8%B2%A8</a>"},{"pid":"bdc3b035cf82f7d720db1d06363a89df0bc5d875","tid":895959,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda8b4de87f717d9084fb6030e1ad571ed2c9c1b","tid":895959,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8bd9496e7eec1f57e09501744d1ad9faa38187","tid":895959,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:40:13.000Z","msg":"又過？"},{"pid":"a8b0d129d250856c7d36d4f5d1555f2c558